×008Articles
========×
Overall  I  think  ×031Ghandy×  did some good job with all
editing,  and  coloring  texts. Some articles are old
but  I  know  how hard it is to check the stuff so no
need  for  an  excuse.  In  the editorial text, he is
writing  a  quite  long "ps" which as writingstyle is
quite  forbidden.  But   that   is   no   big   deal.

